				<li>temperature(TEMPERATURE>30,TEMPERATURE&lt;=44)->Right, but this scorching sun won't let our rooms cool down. It's too hot in here!</li>
				<li>temperature(TEMPERATURE>=16,TEMPERATURE&lt;=30)->A sunny weather is a blessing!</li>
				<li>temperature(TEMPERATURE>5,TEMPERATURE&lt;16)->Yes. And let's hope the sun warms our rooms. It's quite chilly in here.</li>
				<li>temperature(TEMPERATURE>=0,TEMPERATURE&lt;=5)->Yes, but... it's so cold in here I can't work properly[plants]</li>
				<li>temperature(TEMPERATURE>=-10,TEMPERATURE&lt;0)->Sunny and freezing[plants]</li>
				<li>plants(INITIATOR_plants_level&lt;5)->. At least we have a nice crystal blue sky.</li>
				<li>plants(INITIATOR_plants_level>=5)->! Besides, plants out there will almost freeze, for sure.</li>
				<li>plants(INITIATOR_plants_level>=5)->! Where's the good side? Plants will even grow much slower!</li>
